data.description: Great opportunity for an owner or simply as an investment property. Updated units - both up and down - and they are charming, sunlit spaces with newer baths and kitchens, and gorgeous hardwood floors. Fenced yard and a four car garage! Seller's job requires extensive travel and he has a roommate who has been paying $925 a month in the upper unit.  Seller's portion was paying for utilities, new buyer should be able to lease upper level for $1200 +.  Separate elec.  Lower level is recently vacant, but has been rented for the past three years for $1700 a month with one garage and tenant responsible for elec.  Seller has not attempted to get new tenants and will leave that to the new buyer.  Please note that the four car garages have been designated for one per unit, one for owner storage. Neighbor has expressed interest in renting one.
